gate.creole.numbers

Class AnnotationConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • gate.creole.numbers.AnnotationConstants

  • public final class AnnotationConstants
extends Object
    To ensure that all annotations/features created by the different number PRs use the same names this class holds constants specifying the correct values.
    Author:
    Mark A. Greenwood
